  "title": "Educational organizations management system (EOMS)",
  "parse": {
    "text": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external free\" href=\"urn:mrn:iala:dic:0901111e\">urn:mrn:iala:dic:0901111e</a></b>\n</p><p>Educational organizations management system (<span class=\"mw-lingo-term\" data-lingo-term-id=\"c9e2631a1a34db42d515db8e927fd312\">EOMS</span>) is a quality management system for an educational organization. The International Organization for Standardization (<span class=\"mw-lingo-term\" data-lingo-term-id=\"5b512ee8a59deb284ad0a6a035ba10b1\">ISO</span>) has issued <span class=\"mw-lingo-term\" data-lingo-term-id=\"5b512ee8a59deb284ad0a6a035ba10b1\">ISO</span> Standard 21001:2018 on Educational organizations – management systems for educational organizations – requirements with guidance for use.\n</p><p>Source: \n<span class=\"mw-lingo-term\" data-lingo-term-id=\"0a1217bfe27a54fc7e55b72fc62c2371\">IALA</span> Guideline G1014 Accreditation of <span class=\"mw-lingo-term\" data-lingo-term-id=\"df60bf18efe7500adba15a8676604475\">VTS</span> training organizations and approval to deliver <span class=\"mw-lingo-term\" data-lingo-term-id=\"0a1217bfe27a54fc7e55b72fc62c2371\">IALA</span> <span class=\"mw-lingo-term\" data-lingo-term-id=\"df60bf18efe7500adba15a8676604475\">VTS</span> model courses, section 3.1.\n</p><p><br>\n</p>\n<div class=\"LanguageLinks\">\n<table width=\"100%\">\n<tbody><tr valign=\"top\" style=\"background: #FFFFFF\">\n<td style=\"width: 25px; padding-left: 0em; border-right: 1px solid #aaaaaa;border-left: 1px solid #EEF3E2;border-top: 1px solid #EEF3E2;border-bottom: 1px solid #EEF3E2;\"><span typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"/wiki/dictionary/index.php/File:25px-Geographylogo.png\" class=\"mw-file-description\" title=\"Languages\"><img alt=\"Languages\" src=\"/wiki/dictionary/images/8/82/25px-Geographylogo.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"25\" height=\"25\" class=\"mw-file-element\"></a></span></td>\n<td style=\"padding: 1px 1em 0; background: #EEF3E2;\">\n<p><b><a href=\"/wiki/dictionary/index.php/Accident\" title=\"Accident\">English</a></b>\n<span></span>\n<span></span>\n<span></span>\n<span></span>\n</p>\n</td></tr></tbody></table></div></div><div class=\"mw-lingo-tooltip\" id=\"c9e2631a1a34db42d515db8e927fd312\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition navigation-not-searchable\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition-text\">\n<p>Educational organizations – management systems for educational organizations.\n</p>\n</div></div>\n</div><div class=\"mw-lingo-tooltip\" id=\"5b512ee8a59deb284ad0a6a035ba10b1\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition navigation-not-searchable\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition-text\">\n<p>International Standardization Organisation\n</p>\n</div></div>\n</div><div class=\"mw-lingo-tooltip\" id=\"0a1217bfe27a54fc7e55b72fc62c2371\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition navigation-not-searchable\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition-text\">\n<p>International Association of Marine Aids to Navigation and Lighthouse Authorities - AISM\n</p>\n</div></div>\n</div><div class=\"mw-lingo-tooltip\" id=\"df60bf18efe7500adba15a8676604475\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition navigation-not-searchable\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition-text\">\n<p>Vessel Traffic Services\n</p>\n</div></div>\n</div>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260615060443\nCache expiry: 86400\nReduced expiry: false\nComplications: []\nCPU time usage: 0.032 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.045 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 58/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 623/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 112/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/100\nExpensive parser function count: 4/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 0/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   11.148      1 Template:Languages\n100.00%   11.148      1 -total\n 64.14%    7.150      4 Template:Languages/Lang\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key wiki_iala_dictionary_1_41:pcache:idhash:3101-0!can