  "wikitext": "'''urn:mrn:iala:dic:0901111e\n\nEducational organizations management system (EOMS) is a quality management system for an educational organization. The International Organization for Standardization (ISO) has issued ISO Standard 21001:2018 on Educational organizations – management systems for educational organizations – requirements with guidance for use.\n\nSource: \nIALA Guideline G1014 Accreditation of VTS training organizations and approval to deliver IALA VTS model courses, section 3.1.\n\n\n{{languages|Accident}}\n[[Category:9.1 VTS terms]]\n[[Category:Alphabetical Index]]\n[[Category:IALA Dictionary 2023 Revision]]"
